179902.name: Share of global cumulative CO2 emissions from coal
179902.description: Cumulative production-based emissions of carbon dioxide (CO2) from coal since the first year of data availability, measured as a percentage of global cumulative production-based emissions of CO2 from coal since the first year of data availability. This is based on territorial emissions, which do not account for emissions embedded in traded goods. Each country's share of global CO2 emissions from coal has been calculated by Our World in Data using global CO2 emissions from coal provided in the Global Carbon Budget dataset. Global coal emissions include all country emissions.
